_sText:
Just a simple dust themed map. Contains about 15 games:

1)Color

2)Rope

3)Disco

4)Rocky-climb

5)Normal climb

6)Maze/Pacman/Traitor

7)Draw

8)Shark game

9)Volleyball

10)Football

11)Bombgame

12)4Chairs game

13)Hot potato game

14)Dodge ball

15)Breakfloor

It contains some secrets. The map was made to be comfortable for playing.
